'''天主教阿馬總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Ardmachana}}；{{lang-ga|Ard-Deoise Ard Mhacha}}）是[[天主教會|天主教會]]在[[愛爾蘭島|愛爾蘭島]]北部設置的一個[[總教區|總教區]]，相傳是愛爾蘭的開教者[[圣巴特利爵|圣巴特利爵]]於約445年建立的，1152年升格為總教區<ref>{{CathEncy|wstitle=Dublin}}</ref>。管轄範圍包括[[阿馬郡|阿馬郡]]和[[勞斯郡|勞斯郡]]幾乎全部、[[蒂龍郡|蒂龍郡]]大一部，以及[[米斯郡|米斯郡]]和[[倫敦德里郡|倫敦德里郡]]的一部。其首長——'''阿馬總教區總主教'''擁有「{{link-en|愛爾蘭首席主教權|Primacy of Ireland|全愛爾蘭首席主教}}」的榮譽地位。

==現況==

2011年，在當地334,751人口中，有教友227,950人，佔轄區總人口68.1%、61個堂區、186名司鐸、74名修士、286名修女。

現任總主教為{{link-en|愛德門·馬丁|Eamon Martin}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 08.09.2014 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2014/09/08/0617/01373.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-08-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811101922/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2014/09/08/0617/01373.html |archivedate=2019-08-11 |language=en |date=2014-09-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-de|彌額爾·魯特|Michael Router}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 07.05.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/05/07/190507c.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811094606/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/05/07/190507c.html |archivedate=2019-08-11 |language=en |date=2019-05-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為[[若翰·布雷迪|若翰·布雷迪]]<ref>{{cite web |title=BRADY Card. Seán Baptist |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/documentation/cardinali_biografie/cardinali_bio_brady_sb.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811102105/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/documentation/cardinali_biografie/cardinali_bio_brady_sb.html |archivedate=2019-08-11 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

